Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.19,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.35,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:04.91,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.05,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:22.40,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.40,0:01:27.13,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:34.07,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you go. I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you if you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,P-please...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kid with me. What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't go! Please! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that! Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't let you go! I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me. Let go! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama! Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So how was Shinobu's birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Um? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Only three people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko, her mother and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Rich people!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Renting a ball room for a birthday party for three!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually only two. She and her mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your expression says, "I'm depressed"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing really. Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,After the party at the hotel, I stopped by her house. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kaoru-no-Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you run here every weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not usually this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I'm doing extra training for the district basketball tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she was hospitalized for a year. She is so energetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I envy her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so vibrant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That night at Mariko-san's home...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even talk about it to Tomoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Mariko-san going to act then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't think I can bear seeing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,9. Relapse; Broken Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san! When are you coming out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll look like a prune!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko, what on earth were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Good Morning, Nanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,About the day before yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,During first period and even through second period...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...I couldn't look at Mariko-san, sitting right next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say a word to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Or even breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I could smell her subtle scent of Rose cologne,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...and hear her quiet breathing, and my heart sank.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear brother... I couldn't forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to snow tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time you asked me to lunch since we entered Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is... is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It is really a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, of course, Tora wants to lunch with Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tama is a friend of Mike, and Tora, and everyone else too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Tama, you don't have much appetite today...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,See you on the way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro Nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only one true love for me. Only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the world to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Under this shrouded moon, I will jump into the river;
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...with a scream from deep within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry. You are no substitute for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite all your beauty and devotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...you cannot fill my emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Giovanni-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, my dear, won't you come die with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hold on! Where... where does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do? Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I need... could you get me some kind of painkiller?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Painkiller?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Go ask Rei. She should have some. Tell her I need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok... please wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in the clubroom. The basketball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear brother... what's happening to Kaoru-no-Kimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Asaka-san? I don't know... She was here in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,At the theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadn't you heard? She's a guest performer in the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And today the first rehearsal in open to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! We got to come see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This will definitely be a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take these flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.35,0:11:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was moved to tears! I won't be able to sleep tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was no big deal. I messed up three of my lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Juste-sama! It's Kaoru-no-Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please let me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you... cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... she's the one who tricked her way into the Sorority...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:11:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes no difference with whom I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The cold wind blows through my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi is asking for a painkiller! Please give her one of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon to end my life, I look up from the river's side...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...and see a single streak of cloud over a celebrating moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange insects buzz around my ears, and fireflies...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This icy water will be the last warmth I feel during my final moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi needs it. She's suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you die with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you laugh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny! Our friend is suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma cherie La Poupee...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma cherie La Poupee...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A painkiller, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well these are tranquilizers, here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...and a hematogenic, and vitamins...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, found it. Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her not to take too many...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Th... thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma cherie La Poupee, my dear Poupee, who slapped me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Drugs... and more drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint Juste-sama is drenched in drugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'm going now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, see you later...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked for a painkiller. Is it that serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. Very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go. Afternoon classes are starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be resting here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stay right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still recovering, like I said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more stubborn than you look. okay then, but only for fifth period.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How about sports?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you in any sports clubs in junior high?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing in particular...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not talented at sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But the ones I like are tennis, swimming and basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But talent doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm so ordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hospitalized for a long time, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... I have a craving...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...to run very hard... up to the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Until my heart... bursts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My heartbeats...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear them like music, cheerful and happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me realize that just ordinary living is a great thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I feel great...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...and run some more...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...and chase the ball...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I feel much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you come wake me up, after sixth period?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling drowsy like this, I may fall asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:37.45,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Our hopes were too quickly drained there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:45.58,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,The sights during that time and the group's decisions were such that we reported them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother, during sixth period that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:50.37,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,At first we thought that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...I was in another world, removed from both school and Mariko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worrying that whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...worrying that she might wake up in the clubroom, alone, and in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me... where is Kaoru-no-Kimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She left early.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Left early?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She left a note saying "I will be leaving early today".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have had a relapse then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So then... I should get her phone number from the office and call her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, listen, Nanako-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to say something, it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I'm in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Many times, Dear Brother, so many times I called...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...using the number I got from the school office.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if she answered the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I still couldn't really do anything for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanging up the phone would just make me worry more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no answer, and I didn't know what else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, I stopped trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No one understands. Nobody truly understands another.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But someone who cares can still try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that even if we worry about others,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...there is nothing we can really do for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, thank you for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She came here today, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but not for a routine check up; she said she had a sudden pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And? How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Don't concern yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This sort of thing happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain is gone, and she said she was off to a night practice at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good that she plays basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.09,0:21:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean? You mean, while she can?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say such stupid things!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, won't someone explain to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the point of our being born and living?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.68,0:22:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No one truly understands another.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot feel her chest pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So the seriousness of her illness, and what that illness is, I can't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...because no one can truly understand another.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.51,0:22:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But, brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...if someone so alive and vibrant...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.59,0:22:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...has such a sadness and a dark side...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.71,0:23:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She, the very last person I would have guessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot bear the thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Mariko-san. You should eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, Mariko...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.28,0:23:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the hell out of my life !
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.49,0:23:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.85,0:24:14.05,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:19.52,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.99,0:24:25.13,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.13,0:24:30.60,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.34,0:24:36.87,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.87,0:24:42.35,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.35,0:24:45.08,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.08,0:24:47.89,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.89,0:24:50.29,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.29,0:24:55.56,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.43,0:25:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako continues to shun Mariko.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.98,0:25:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, Mariko suddenly faints while at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.98,0:25:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When Nanako goes to Mariko's house to let her mother know,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.41,0:25:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako learns about Mariko's shocking secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.58,0:25:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Mariko
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.95,0:25:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
